DESCRIPTION: Changes the weapon the character is using into another one they own.



Type: POST



INPUT:
{
    "id": ...
}

"id" -> uint // The id of the weapon replacing the current one



RETURNS:
{
    "alive": ...
}

"alive" -> bool // False if the character is not alive



ERRORS:
400 (Bad request)
    Cause: Malformed JSON

401 (Unauthorized)
    Cause: Bad credentials

500 (Internal server error)
    Cause: Internal error
